author: Russell Brand
description:
Peter Thiel says the real threat isn’t AI or nuclear war — it’s one world government. In this Unpacked, I explore Thiel’s warnings, the eerie overlap with biblical prophecy, and the terrifying rise of biochemical surveillance. Are we sleepwalking into a future where a godless, centralized power controls our cities, our bodies, and even our thoughts?

[UNPACKED]
